\v 34 ὃν γὰρ ἀπέστειλεν ὁ θεὸς τὰ ῥήματα τοῦ θεοῦ λαλεῖ, οὐ γὰρ ἐκ μέτρου δίδωσιν τὸ πνεῦμα\f 5 \fr 34 \ft {B} \fk τὸ πνεῦμα \ft \zapy P\zup 66, 75\zup* א B\zup 2\zup* C\zup *\zup* L W\zup supp\zup* Θ 083 0141 ƒ\zup 1\zup* 33 205 565 579 597 1241 it\zup b, e, f\zup2 c\zup , l\zup* Origen\zup gr\zup* Cyril; Victorinus-Pettau\zup 1/2\zup* // \fk ὁ θεὸς τὸ πνεῦμα \ft A C\zup 2\zup* D Δ Ψ 086 ƒ\zup 13\zup* 28 157 180 700 892 1006 1010 1071 1243 1292 1342 1424 1505 \it Byz\it* [E F G H] it\zup a, aur, (c), (d), f*, j, π, q, r\zup2 1\zup2* (it\zup ff\zup2 2\zup2* \fk τοῦ θεοῦ\ft ) vg syr\zup p, h\zup* cop\zup sa, bo, fay\zup* arm eth geo slav Origen\zup lat\zup* Didymus\zup dub\zup* Chrysostom; Victorinus-Pettau\zup 1/2vid\zup* Gregory-Elvira\zup vid\zup* Jerome Augustine // \it omit\it* B\zup *\zup*\f*.
