\v 23 ἐγὼ ἐν αὐτοῖς καὶ σὺ ἐν ἐμοί, ἵνα ὦσιν τετελειωμένοι εἰς ἕν, ἵνα γινώσκῃ ὁ κόσμος ὅτι σύ με ἀπέστειλας καὶ ἠγάπησας\f 6 \fr 23 \ft {A} \fk ἠγάπησας \ft א B C L W Δ Θ Ψ ƒ\zup 1\zup* ƒ\zup 13\zup* 33 157 180 205 565 597 700 1006 1010 1071 1241 1292 1342 1505 \it Byz\it* [E G H N]\it Lect\it* it\zup c, e, f, q\zup* vg syr\zup h\zup2 mg\zup2* cop\zup sa, pbo, bo\zup2 pt\zup2* slav Clement Eusebius Gregory-Nyssa Cyril; Ambrose Jerome\zup 1/2\zup* Augustine // \fk ἠγάπησα \ft D 0141 892\zup supp\zup* 1243 1424 \it l\it*~387\zup 1/2\zup* \it l\it*~1016\zup 1/2\zup* \it l\it*~1552\zup 1/2\zup* it\zup a, aur, b, d, r\zup2 1\zup2* vg\zup mss\zup* syr\zup p, h, pal\zup2 ms\zup2* cop\zup bo\zup2 pt\zup2* arm eth geo Chrysostom; Jerome\zup 1/2\zup*\f* αὐτοὺς καθὼς ἐμὲ ἠγάπησας.\f g \fr 23 \ft P: NA TEV FC NIV VP Lu NJB REB\f*
