\v 25 \x * \xo 25 \xt Jn 3.15; 6.40\x* καὶ αὕτη ἐστὶν ἡ ἐπαγγελία ἣν αὐτὸς ἐπηγγείλατο ἡμῖν\f 6 \fr 25 \ft {A} \fk ἡμῖν \ft א A C Ψ 33 81 322 323 436 945 1067 1175 1243 1292\zup c\zup* 1409 1505 1611 1735 1739 1844 1852 2138 2298 2344 2464 \it Byz\it* [K L P] \it Lect\it* it\zup ar, h, l, t\zup* vg syr\zup p, h\zup* cop\zup sa, bo\zup* arm eth geo slav Ambrose Augustine // \fk ὑμῖν \ft B 1241 1292\zup *\zup* 1881 \it l\it* 1441 vg\zup mss\zup*\f*, τὴν ζωὴν τὴν αἰώνιον.\f n \fr 25 \ft NO P: TR AD Lu NJB TOB // SP: WH\f*
